cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL 

This paper focuses on depth completion for driving scenarios using lidar and stereo cameras. Therefore, the most likely category is computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also deals with robotics (cs.RO) as it is related to autonomous driving. Machine learning (cs.LG) is also a possible category as the paper proposes a new method for depth completion. Artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and computational linguistics (cs.CL) are less likely categories as they are not directly related to the topic of the paper.
